<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

    <title>
      {%- if template == 'index' -%}
        BaseCode Health — Built for Your Biology
      {%- elsif template contains 'product' -%}
        {{ product.title }} — Probiotic Informed by Biological Diversity Research | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template == '404' -%}
        Page Not Found | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-estrogen' -%}
        Estrogen Balance Starts in Your Gut | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-testosterone' -%}
        Your Testosterone Problem Starts in Your Gut | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-joint-pain' -%}
        Joint Pain Is Gut Inflammation | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-brain-fog' -%}
        Brain Fog Starts in Your Gut | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-bloating' -%}
        Bloating After Dietary Change? It's Your Microbiome | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-body-odor' -%}
        Body Odor Is a Gut Problem | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-food-sensitivities' -%}
        Food Sensitivities Start in Your Microbiome | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-skin' -%}
        Your Skin Problems Start in Your Gut | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'quiz' -%}
        Biology Score — Free 2-Minute Quiz | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'free-report' -%}
        The Biology Gap — Free Research Report | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'about' -%}
        About BaseCode Health — Built for Your Biology
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'science' -%}
        The Science — Biological Diversity Research | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'faq' -%}
        Frequently Asked Questions | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'contact' -%}
        Contact Us | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template contains 'collection' -%}
        {{ collection.title }} | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template contains 'blog' -%}
        {{ blog.title }} | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template contains 'article' -%}
        {{ article.title }} | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template == 'cart' -%}
        Your Cart | BaseCode Health
      {%- elsif template == 'search' -%}
        Search Results | BaseCode Health
      {%- else -%}
        {{ page_title }} | BaseCode Health
      {%- endif -%}
    </title>

    {%- capture seo_description -%}
      {%- if template == 'index' -%}
        Your biology is unique — your supplements should be too. Origin is the first probiotic designed for your unique biology. 40B CFU, 4 strains, MAKTREK Bi-Pass delivery. From $34/mo.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-estrogen' -%}
        Your gut controls estrogen metabolism through the estrobolome. When key bacteria deplete, hot flashes, mood swings, and weight gain follow. Origin supports the gut foundation your hormones depend on.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-testosterone' -%}
        Your gut bacteria regulate testosterone through the HPG axis. When your microbiome shifts, energy, strength, and drive decline. Origin supports the gut-testosterone connection.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-joint-pain' -%}
        Joint pain isn't aging — it's gut-driven inflammation. When your intestinal barrier weakens, endotoxins trigger chronic inflammation. Origin restores barrier integrity with 4 targeted strains.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-brain-fog' -%}
        Brain fog isn't burnout. It's your gut leaking inflammation into your brain via the gut-brain axis. Origin delivers 4 strains that support neuroinflammation reduction and mental clarity.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-bloating' -%}
        Chronic bloating after dietary changes? Your gut bacteria lost the enzymes to digest your food. Origin restores the bacterial community your digestion depends on.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-body-odor' -%}
        Body odor is a metabolic processing problem that starts in your gut. When key bacteria deplete, volatile compounds build up. Origin supports the metabolic pathways that neutralize them.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-food-sensitivities' -%}
        Food sensitivities develop when your gut bacteria lose the enzymes to digest certain foods. Origin restores bacterial enzyme production so you can eat the foods you love again.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'landing-skin' -%}
        Acne, eczema, and psoriasis often start in the gut, not the skin. The gut-skin axis drives inflammatory skin conditions. Origin supports the gut foundation your skin depends on.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'quiz' -%}
        Take the free 2-minute Biology Score quiz. 7 research-backed questions to assess your microbiome depletion risk. Instant results, no email required.
      {%- elsif template.suffix == 'free-report' -%}
        Download The Biology Gap — a free 6-page research report covering the HELIUS study, microbiome depletion, and why biological diversity demands a different approach to supplementation.
      {%- elsif page_description != blank -%}
        {{ page_description }}
      {%- else -%}
        Origin is the first probiotic informed by biological diversity research. 40B CFU, 4 strains, MAKTREK Bi-Pass delivery, FOS prebiotic. From $34/mo.
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endcapture -%}
    <meta name="description" content="{{ seo_description | strip_newlines | strip }}">
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{ canonical_url }}">

    {%- if settings.favicon != blank -%}
      <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="{{ settings.favicon | image_url: width: 32 }}">
    {%- endif -%}

    <!-- Preconnects -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.shopify.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

    <!-- Google Fonts: Inter (body) + Instrument Sans (headings) -->
    <link rel="preload" as="style" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" onload="this.onload=null;this.rel='stylesheet'">
    <noscript><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"></noscript>

    <!-- Theme CSS -->
    {{ 'base.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

    <!-- Theme settings → CSS custom properties bridge -->
    <style>
      :root {
        {%- if settings.color_primary != blank -%}--color-primary: {{ settings.color_primary }};{%- endif -%}
        {%- if settings.color_accent != blank -%}--color-accent: {{ settings.color_accent }};{%- endif -%}
        {%- if settings.color_cream != blank -%}--color-cream: {{ settings.color_cream }};{%- endif -%}
        {%- if settings.color_text != blank -%}--color-text: {{ settings.color_text }};{%- endif -%}
        {%- if settings.color_text_light != blank -%}--color-text-light: {{ settings.color_text_light }};{%- endif -%}
        --color-bg-primary: var(--color-primary);
        --color-bg-cream: var(--color-cream);
        --color-bg-accent: var(--color-accent);
      }
    </style>

    <!-- SEO meta -->
    <meta name="author" content="BaseCode Health">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="{{ settings.color_primary | default: '#1C2E23' }}">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <meta name="referrer" content="strict-origin-when-cross-origin">

    <!-- Open Graph -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="{% if template contains 'product' %}product{% elsif template contains 'article' %}article{% else %}website{% endif %}">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{ canonical_url }}">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="BaseCode Health">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{ page_title }}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{ seo_description | strip_newlines | strip }}">
    {%- if settings.og_image != blank -%}
      <meta property="og:image" content="{{ settings.og_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}">
      <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200">
      <meta property="og:image:height" content="630">
    {%- endif -%}

    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:site" content="@BaseCodeHealth">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ page_title }}">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ seo_description | strip_newlines | strip }}">
    {%- if settings.og_image != blank -%}
      <meta name="twitter:image" content="{{ settings.og_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}">
    {%- endif -%}

    <!-- Google Analytics 4 -->
    {%- if settings.ga4_id != blank -%}
      {% render 'ga4-tag' %}
    {%- endif -%}

    <!-- Meta Pixel -->
    {%- if settings.meta_pixel_id != blank -%}
      {% render 'meta-pixel' %}
    {%- endif -%}

    <!-- JSON-LD Structured Data -->
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "@id": "{{ shop.url }}/#organization",
          "name": "BaseCode Health",
          "url": "{{ shop.url }}",
          "description": "Supplements informed by biological diversity research. Your biology isn't one-size-fits-all.",
          "email": "hello@basecodehealth.com",
          "foundingDate": "2025",
          "sameAs": [
            "https://www.instagram.com/basecodehealth",
            "https://x.com/BaseCodeHealth"
          ]
        },
        {
          "@type": "WebSite",
          "@id": "{{ shop.url }}/#website",
          "name": "BaseCode Health",
          "url": "{{ shop.url }}",
          "publisher": { "@id": "{{ shop.url }}/#organization" },
          "potentialAction": {
            "@type": "SearchAction",
            "target": "{{ shop.url }}/search?q={search_term_string}",
            "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"
          }
        }
        {%- if template contains 'product' -%}
        ,{
          "@type": "Product",
          "@id": "{{ shop.url }}/#product",
          "name": "{{ product.title }}",
          "brand": { "@type": "Brand", "name": "BaseCode Health" },
          "description": "{{ product.description | strip_html | truncate: 250 }}",
          "sku": "{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.sku }}",
          "url": "{{ shop.url }}{{ product.url }}",
          "image": "{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}",
          "offers": {
            "@type": "Offer",
            "availability": "{% if product.available %}https://schema.org/InStock{% else %}https://schema.org/OutOfStock{% endif %}",
            "url": "{{ shop.url }}{{ product.url }}",
            "price": "{{ product.price | money_without_currency }}",
            "priceCurrency": "{{ shop.currency }}"
          }
        }
        {%- endif -%}
      ]
    }
    </script>

    {{ content_for_header }}

    <noscript>
      <style>
        .reveal-hidden, .reveal-left, .reveal-right, .animate-fade, .stagger-children > * {
          opacity: 1 !important;
          transform: none !important;
        }
      </style>
    </noscript>
  </head>

  <body class="template-{{ template | replace: '.', '-' }}" data-template="{{ template }}">
    <!-- Meta Pixel noscript fallback -->
    {%- if settings.meta_pixel_id != blank -%}
      <noscript><img height="1" width="1" style="display:none" src="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id={{ settings.meta_pixel_id }}&ev=PageView&noscript=1"></noscript>
    {%- endif -%}

    <!-- Skip navigation -->
    <a href="#main-content" class="skip-nav">Skip to content</a>

    {% sections 'header-group' %}

    <main id="main-content" role="main">
      {{ content_for_layout }}
    </main>

    {% sections 'footer-group' %}

    <!-- Cart Drawer -->
    {% render 'cart-drawer' %}

    <!-- Theme JS -->
    <script src="{{ 'theme.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

    <!-- Tracking events helper -->
    {% render 'tracking-events' %}
  </body>
</html>
